{
  "name": "smile-contracts",
  "description": "Smile is a non-custodial, parametric options marketplace that combines 1inch Aqua, Uniswap v4 Hooks, and Chainlink CRE so LPs can quote an entire strike range from one capital pool while their collateral keeps earning DeFi yield. This repository is a monorepo containing the Foundry-based Solidity contracts, a Next.js/TypeScript frontend, and a Chainlink CRE settlement workflow.",
